  <main>
    <section identifier="/ca-mountain-view/part-i/article-v/section-506"
             temporalId="sSection 506">
      <num>Section 506</num>
      <heading>Powers vested in the council</heading>
      <content>
        <p>All powers of the city, except as otherwise provided in this Charter, shall be vested
               in the council, and said council may establish the method by which any of such powers
               may be exercised.</p>
      </content>
    </section>
  </main>
